<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٣٤٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3106">عَبَّادُ بْنُ عَبَّادٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3037">عَاصِمٌ الْأَحْوَلُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«حَالَفَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بَيْنَ الْأَنْصَارِ وَقُرَيْشٍ فِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دَارِي الَّتِي بِالْمَدِينَةِ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٣٤١ - وَقَنَتَ شَهْرًا يَدْعُو عَلَى أَحْيَاءٍ مِنْ بَنِي سُلَيْمٍ.»<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>